#
# Known limitations within Chopstix

- Phone extension can be a maximum of 5 digits
- If order exceeds $999.99, subtotal labels will not line up
- Maximum dollar value for any item or total is $21,474,836.47
- Fractional accounting of pennies does not happen
- Only North-American telephone numbers are permitted
- 250 on-screen rows maximum
- 4K order item maximum
- 64 subitems per item maximum
- printer errors allow a posted order to be modified and reprinted without
  updating the database
